Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: British city riots
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wgjd
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Jul 1981
Warning for Reagan as observers blame Thatcher's economic policies for outbreak of riots. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less